extends ./layout.jade

block vars
  - var title = 'About'

block content

  div.container
    h1 About Us
    div.row
      div.col-sm-3
        //div.myImg
        img(src="/images/aboutme.png", alt="generic placeholder image", height="350px", width="250px")
      div.col-sm-6
        p.
          Kolotylo Fitness is a online personalized training system. The goal of Kolotylo fitness is transformation for every client. Kolotylo fitness offers programs for both fat loss and muscle gain. The programs are all 12 weeks. You tell us how many times you can make the gym per week and we will make the schedule around your availability. Specifically designed with the best and most effective exercises, rep ranges and amount of sets to perform so you get the best results possible, and the most out of every workout. The workouts designed at Kolotylo fitness are scientifically proven to help you burn as much fat as possible, while building muscle.
        p.
          Once you purchase the package, Kolotylo fitness will be in contact with you in within 24 hours. You will need to fill out a questionnaire. After getting to know you, we will make a package for you. At Kolotylo fitness we are so confident in our packages, that we offer money back if you are not satisfied. If you complete the program and are not satisfied with the results then you will get a full refund. After purchasing the package we will be available anytime for coaching via email. LET US HELP YOU ACHIEVE YOUR DREAM BODY!
      
      //Contact Form Template
      div.col-sm-3
        div.well.well-sm
          form.form-horizontal(method='post')
            fieldset
              legend.text-center.header Contact Us
              div.form-group
                div.col-md-12.text-center
                  input#name.form-control(name='name', type='text', placeholder='Name')
              div.form-group
                div.col-md-12.text-center
                  input#email.form-control(name='email', type='text', placeholder='Email Address')
              div.form-group
                div.col-md-12.text-center
                  input#phone.form-control(name='phone', type='text', placeholder='Phone')
              div.form-group
                div.col-md-12.text-center
                  textarea#message.form-control(name='message', placeholder='If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to leave your message here. We will get back to you within 24 hours.', rows='7')
              div.form-group
                div.col-md-12.text-center
                  button.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(type='submit') Submit



